ELE DEIXOU SUA OPINIÃO BEM CLARA.

517
00:37:26,420 --> 00:37:29,780
APENAS RELAXE, SR. SUMMERSON.

518
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:31,140
O QUE ELE DISSE?

519
00:37:31,340 --> 00:37:33,220
F...
TOSSE.

520
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:38,100
AH, QUERIDO.

521
00:37:38,300 --> 00:37:39,340
OLÁ?

522
00:37:39,540 --> 00:37:43,140
