523
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:48,380
CERTO.

524
00:37:51,580 --> 00:37:53,980
VOCÊ QUERIA ME VER?

525
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:56,660
SIM. MOLLY...

526
00:37:56,860 --> 00:38:00,980
SIM?
VOCÊ...

